---

---

<section class='steps' id='how-it-works'>
  <div class='wrapper'>
    <div class='steps-header' data-aos='fade-up'>
      <span class='steps-label'>Cómo funciona</span>
      <h2 class='steps-title'>
        3 pasos simples para tener tu <span>catálogo activo</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class='steps-timeline'>
      <div class='steps-line'></div>

      <div class='step' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='100'>
        <div class='step-number-wrap'>
          <div class='step-number'>1</div>
        </div>
        <div class='step-content'>
          <h3 class='step-title'>Asegura tu lugar</h3>
          <p class='step-text'>
            Realiza el pago de preventa vía Stripe. Tu lugar quedará reservado y serás parte del
            grupo exclusivo de fundadores.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='step' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='200'>
        <div class='step-number-wrap'>
          <div class='step-number'>2</div>
        </div>
        <div class='step-content'>
          <h3 class='step-title'>Nos das tu info</h3>
          <p class='step-text'>
            Te contactaremos por WhatsApp para recibir tus fotos, productos y precios. Nosotros nos
            encargamos de todo lo técnico.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='step' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='300'>
        <div class='step-number-wrap'>
          <div class='step-number'>3</div>
        </div>
        <div class='step-content'>
          <h3 class='step-title'>¡Lanzamiento!</h3>
          <p class='step-text'>
            Tu catálogo estará activo antes que el de tu competencia. Comparte el link con tus
            clientes y empieza a recibir pedidos organizados.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .steps {
    padding: 6rem 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f5f0f0 0%, var(--neutral-02) 50%, #f5f0f0 100%);
    position: relative;
  }

  .steps-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }

  .steps-label {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.15);
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .steps-title {
    font-size: var(--48-pt);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--shade-03);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .steps-title span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--shade-03));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .steps-timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .steps-line {
    position: absolute;
    left: 32px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary), var(--shade-03));
    opacity: 0.25;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-number-wrap {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--shade-03));
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.25);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .step-number {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .step-content {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    flex: 1;
    transition:
      transform 0.3s ease,
      box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step-content:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--shade-03);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .step-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--shade-04);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .steps {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .steps-title {
      font-size: var(--40-pt);
    }

    .steps-line {
      left: 24px;
    }

    .step-number-wrap {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
    }

    .step-number {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .step-content {
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .step {
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
